modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod makes zombies not able to dig. Zombies can destroy blocks and jump (vanilla values).
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod makes [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) not able to dig. Zombies can destroy blocks and jump (vanilla values).

This mod does not work with [Zombie Modification Mod](https://7daystodiemods.com/zombie-modification-for-a18/).
